        <abstract> 
<p>CD is glad to hear that EK plans a short historical discussion on evolution [in <hi rend="italic">Erasmus Darwin</hi>],</p>  
<p>but hopes he will not spend much powder and shot on Butler – his ephemeral work is not worth it. Sends a review [of <hi rend="italic">Evolution, old and new</hi>].</p> 
